{"id": "1216593693889269830", "channel_id": "1215696847981781012", "type": 0, "author_id": "1051752197244866681", "author_name": "iceyss_", "author_bot": false, "content": "融灾的debuff和怪物的伤害成长从根本上就是在拒绝慢速队伍，特别点名那个狂气递增和50盾上限的debuff，平时的高压本我能拿阿格里帕蛹脐带加蛹叠戒备跟对面拖，进了融灾大招越来越难开不说盾还只能叠一半，对面还疯狂涨伤害，这种情况下我直接掏希洛莉莉跟对面爆了完事我还用什么慢速阵容，至于深潜那更不说了竞速环境更不可能用慢速阵容", "timestamp": "2024-03-11T03:48:59.841000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1215696847981781012", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅關於「幻夢深潛」的再度調整說明", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1216595479240900799", "channel_id": "1215696847981781012", "type": 19, "author_id": "1051752197244866681", "author_name": "iceyss_", "author_bot": false, "content": "疯狂的上伤害压力和压缩生存空间并不能驱使大家选择生存阵容，因为你游有些boss的伤害成长数值太变态了，一旦再从机制和数值上压缩了生存空间，生存队只会更尴尬，我既然拖不住那我为什么不跟对面爆了，最后还是会回过头去选择伤害强项的阵容", "timestamp": "2024-03-11T03:56:05.502000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["633215996508766229"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1216057309738827877", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1215696847981781012", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅關於「幻夢深潛」的再度調整說明", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1216616603521650688", "channel_id": "1215696847981781012", "type": 19, "author_id": "232848201500065792", "author_name": "hananichiya", "author_bot": false, "content": "因為黑潮有前六回合王會鎖血的機制阿揪咪", "timestamp": "2024-03-11T05:20:01.923000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1051752197244866681"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1216595479240900799", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1215696847981781012", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅關於「幻夢深潛」的再度調整說明", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1216651084324667413", "channel_id": "1215696847981781012", "type": 0, "author_id": "453161298931482626", "author_name": "nightmorals", "author_bot": false, "content": "<@633215996508766229> 開個測試服吧，比起連自己做了什麼都不確定就釋出、不如好好測試再出來，你們人手就已經很缺了、沒辦法全力測試了，又不開放玩家幫忙、而扔上正式伺服器讓大家一起受苦，何必呢，就算像這樣開串讓人討論，只有文字也遠遠比不上親自下場體驗來的直觀。這樣改來改去不管是玩家或你們都很累啊", "timestamp": "2024-03-11T07:37:02.787000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-03-11T07:38:48.547000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": ["633215996508766229"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1215696847981781012", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅關於「幻夢深潛」的再度調整說明", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1216651934191321129", "channel_id": "1215696847981781012", "type": 0, "author_id": "453161298931482626", "author_name": "nightmorals", "author_bot": false, "content": "作為一個服務型遊戲，未來還有那麼多的內容要弄，卻一直花時間在既有系統上的反覆調適未免太浪費力氣了，這樣真的有辦法好好準備以後的活動嗎", "timestamp": "2024-03-11T07:40:25.411000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-03-11T07:41:19.531000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1215696847981781012", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅關於「幻夢深潛」的再度調整說明", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1216664314870501427", "channel_id": "1215696847981781012", "type": 19, "author_id": "633215996508766229", "author_name": "game.producer.light", "author_bot": false, "content": "測試服我們評估過狀況，並不適合我們當下。與大家想的不一樣的是，每個系統我們是較為獨立的成員跟進的。一個系統在調整時不一定會影響其他。尤其是調整是比新製作更快。也正是因為這個，新活動已經快來臨了！", "timestamp": "2024-03-11T08:29:37.195000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["453161298931482626"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1216651934191321129", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1215696847981781012", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅關於「幻夢深潛」的再度調整說明", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1216670965308850276", "channel_id": "1215696847981781012", "type": 19, "author_id": "1180456731143327794", "author_name": "su_su_su0216", "author_bot": false, "content": "蹲个新活动预告🍟", "timestamp": "2024-03-11T08:56:02.783000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["633215996508766229"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1216664314870501427", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1215696847981781012", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅關於「幻夢深潛」的再度調整說明", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1216703917484802178", "channel_id": "1215696847981781012", "type": 19, "author_id": "1051752197244866681", "author_name": "iceyss_", "author_bot": false, "content": "但事实就是扛前六回合就算是输出偏向类阵容也不会有太大压力，因为这个时候boss的成长性还没飚起来，等到boss的伤害飚起来了融灾环境里慢速阵容反而就尬住了，因为你又跟对面爆不了又被debuff限制的拖不住", "timestamp": "2024-03-11T11:06:59.194000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["232848201500065792"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1216616603521650688", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1215696847981781012", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅關於「幻夢深潛」的再度調整說明", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1216709081134403644", "channel_id": "1215696847981781012", "type": 0, "author_id": "1213843511707705425", "author_name": "huangegjg", "author_bot": false, "content": "融灾狂气消耗增加无上限，真是个天才设计", "timestamp": "2024-03-11T11:27:30.304000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1215696847981781012", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅關於「幻夢深潛」的再度調整說明", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1216759135878643773", "channel_id": "1215696847981781012", "type": 19, "author_id": "453161298931482626", "author_name": "nightmorals", "author_bot": false, "content": "好吧好吧，反正不是第一次反覆橫跳，以後想必也還會有更多次，認了。\n也是啦，有台港澳服這個大型測試服能用，再開一個真正的測試服確實「不適合當下」啦", "timestamp": "2024-03-11T14:46:24.285000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["633215996508766229"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1216664314870501427", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1215696847981781012", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅關於「幻夢深潛」的再度調整說明", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
